    <div class="large-6 columns">
    <h4>This is a content section.</h4>
    <p>At the Bug we feature a variety of lodgings to suit any budget.
       From well appointed private rooms in cabins, vacation rentals,
      to tent cabins and Hostelling International licensed hostel dorms. </p>
     <p>
      Our guests are welcome at the June Bug Cafe offering fresh comfort
      and international foods. The Cafe features a daily crafted dinner menu,
      highlighting our garden, local or organic ingredients. There are always vegan,
       vegetarian options and holiday feast menus. Breakfast & lunch are solid
       choices for your active day. Or, enjoy the fully equipped guest kitchen.
        Both have free wi-fi and are well stocked with board games, darts,
       ping pong, books and lively conversation with diverse guests and locals.
     </p>
